{"id":259098,"url":"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Happiness_(movie)","text":"\"Happiness\" is a 1998 American comedy drama movie. It stars Jane Adams, Jon Lovitz, Philip Seymour Hoffman, Dylan Baker and Lara Flynn Boyle. It was directed by Todd Solondz. The movie was first rated NC-17. This caused problems with the advertising and distribution of the movie. Because of this, they chose to release the movie without any rating.\nThe movie was nominated for a Golden Globe Award for \"Best Screenplay\" (Todd Solondz).","categories":[],"infobox_types":[],"annotations":[{"uri":"United_States","surface_form":"American","offset":22},{"uri":"Comedy_movie","surface_form":"comedy","offset":31},{"uri":"Drama_movie","surface_form":"drama movie","offset":38},{"uri":"Cast_member","surface_form":"stars","offset":54},{"uri":"Jane_Adams","surface_form":"Jane Adams","offset":60},{"uri":"Jon_Lovitz","surface_form":"Jon Lovitz","offset":72},{"uri":"Philip_Seymour_Hoffman","surface_form":"Philip Seymour Hoffman","offset":84},{"uri":"Dylan_Baker","surface_form":"Dylan Baker","offset":108},{"uri":"Lara_Flynn_Boyle","surface_form":"Lara Flynn Boyle","offset":124},{"uri":"Movie_director","surface_form":"directed","offset":149},{"uri":"Todd_Solondz","surface_form":"Todd Solondz","offset":161},{"uri":"Motion_Picture_Association_of_America_film_rating_system","surface_form":"rated","offset":195},{"uri":"NC-17","surface_form":"NC-17","offset":201},{"uri":"Advertisement","surface_form":"advertising","offset":238},{"uri":"Distribution","surface_form":"distribution","offset":254},{"uri":"Nominate","surface_form":"nominated","offset":364},{"uri":"Golden_Globe_Award","surface_form":"Golden Globe Award","offset":380},{"uri":"Screenplay","surface_form":"Screenplay","offset":409}]}